Subject: Re: [Antenna-discussion] crystal radios, loop antennas,ferrite =

antennas

Simple answer: The ferrite rod antenna is much more compact.  For a crystal =

set, the loop is typically about a square meter in area, or more.

John Bordelon, K4JIU
Marietta, GA 30066




